{"pageProps":{"data":{"news_id":"286","news_catgory":"1","hot_news":"0","news_push":"","news_on_top":"1","news_title":"印度大力發展可再生能源 與日本聯手「去碳化」","news_summary":"","image_path":"","news_des":null,"news_content":"<p style='margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19.2px; line-height: 2; font-family: Helvetica, &quot;Noto Sans CJK TC&quot;, &quot;PingFang TC&quot;, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);'>日本經濟產業大臣世耕弘成在印度參與「日印能源對話」，兩國確定全方位合作，在印度推廣可再生能源，以實現「去碳化」目標，大幅減少二氧化碳排放。</p>\n\n<p style='margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19.2px; line-height: 2; font-family: Helvetica, &quot;Noto Sans CJK TC&quot;, &quot;PingFang TC&quot;, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);'>印度的電力基礎設施不足，不少城鄉都沒有連上大型電網，只能靠當地的柴油發電機發電，嚴重污染環境。</p>\n\n<p style='margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19.2px; line-height: 2; font-family: Helvetica, &quot;Noto Sans CJK TC&quot;, &quot;PingFang TC&quot;, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);'>印度電力部長辛格（R.K. Singh）與世耕弘成，在「日印能源對話」達成了「日印能源轉換合作計劃」。兩國除了在太陽能等可再生能源領域合作，讓電力供應更穩定之外，還合作範圍還包括氫氣運用以及電動車充電設備等。</p>\n\n<p style='margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19.2px; line-height: 2; font-family: Helvetica, &quot;Noto Sans CJK TC&quot;, &quot;PingFang TC&quot;, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);'>兩國還計劃結合日本技術與印度人才，組成團隊進軍非洲市場。</p>\n\n<p style='margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19.2px; line-height: 2; font-family: Helvetica, &quot;Noto Sans CJK TC&quot;, &quot;PingFang TC&quot;, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);'>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style='margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19.2px; line-height: 2; font-family: Helvetica, &quot;Noto Sans CJK TC&quot;, &quot;PingFang TC&quot;, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);'>資料來源:http://e-info.org.tw/node/211388</p>\n","keyword":"","news_order_id":"0","create_date":"2018-05-28","clk_count":"119"}},"__N_SSG":true}